<!-- FAQ -->
<section style="position:relative; padding:80px 0; background:var(--deep); overflow:hidden;">
  <div class="bubbles" id="b5" data-bubbles="6"></div>
  <div class="content-wrap" style="position:relative; z-index:2; max-width:720px; margin:0 auto;">
    <div class="section-tag reveal" style="text-align:center;">FAQ</div>
    <h2 class="reveal reveal-delay-1" style="font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:clamp(24px,3vw,40px); letter-spacing:2px; text-transform:uppercase; text-align:center; margin-bottom:48px;">
      Common Questions
    </h2>

    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:2px;">

      <div style="background:var(--card-bg); border:1px solid var(--border); padding:24px 28px;">
        <div style="font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:1px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:10px;">How quickly can a diver be dispatched?</div>
        <p style="color:var(--fog); font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; margin:0;">Most jobs are accepted within hours of payment confirmation. Scheduling depends on your preferred date and diver availability in your area. Rush requests can be noted in the job description.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="background:var(--card-bg); border:1px solid var(--border); padding:24px 28px;">
        <div style="font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:1px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:10px;">What if no diver is available in my area?</div>
        <p style="color:var(--fog); font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; margin:0;">If your job doesn't get accepted within 48 hours, the Hero team will reach out directly to arrange an alternative. You are never charged until a diver confirms.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="background:var(--card-bg); border:1px solid var(--border); padding:24px 28px;">
        <div style="font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:1px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:10px;">Can I get an inspection for a dock or marina, not a vessel?</div>
        <p style="color:var(--fog); font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; margin:0;">Absolutely. Select "Full Underwater Survey" or "Custom Request" as the job type and describe the structure in the notes. Pilings, seawalls, breakwaters, and marina basins are all within scope.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="background:var(--card-bg); border:1px solid var(--border); padding:24px 28px;">
        <div style="font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:1px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:10px;">What format is the report delivered in?</div>
        <p style="color:var(--fog); font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; margin:0;">Reports are emailed as a professional branded HTML document and are permanently archived in your Hero account. You can view, download, and print them at any time.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="background:var(--card-bg); border:1px solid var(--border); padding:24px 28px;">
        <div style="font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif; font-size:16px; letter-spacing:1px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:10px;">Is payment secure?</div>
        <p style="color:var(--fog); font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; margin:0;">All payments are processed through Stripe, the industry standard for secure online payments. Hero never stores your card details.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

