    <h2 class="reveal" style="font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,56px); letter-spacing:3px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:16px;">Ready to Request?</h2>
    <p class="reveal reveal-delay-1" style="color:rgba(240,244,248,0.8); font-size:18px; margin-bottom:36px; max-width:480px; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto; line-height:1.6;">Create your free account and have a certified diver in the water within 24 hours.</p>
    <a href="https://hero-diver-portal.netlify.app/signup.html" class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="display:inline-block; padding:16px 48px; background:var(--white); color:var(--signal-red); font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:15px; letter-spacing:3px; text-transform:uppercase; text-decoration:none; clip-path:polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 96% 100%, 0 100%); padding-right:56px;">Get Started →</a>
  </div>
</section>
